item.text: The narrative chart is an attempt at providing an alternative view of how a page has evolved within the federation. While it is still a work in progress, an early version is available but there are no automatic links yet.
Also see [[Visualizing Page History]] for a view on how the 'narrative chart' has evolved.
The basic URL to load the narrative chart is [http://fedwiki.rodwell.me/narrative/] however this just loads the page code and renders an empty view as it has not been told what to show.

The basic URL to load the narrative chart is [http://fedwiki.rodwell.me/narrative/ http://fedwiki.rodwell.me/narrative/] however this just loads the page code and renders an empty view as it has not been told what to show.
To tell the narrative chart which page we wish to display the history of, and which sites we want to start from we need to append some parameters.
#pagename@site1@site2...
#pagename@site1@site2...
Using the
#pagename@site1@site2...
#<pagename>@<site1>[@site2...]
We replace <pagename> with the name of the page we are interested in.
We replace <pagename> with the name of the page we are interested in, <site> with the site we want to start from. We can also add extra sites, by adding them after the first.
#<pagename>@<site1>
#<pagename>@<site>
#pagename@site1@site2
#pagename@site
We replace 'pagename' with the name of the page we are interested in, 'site' with the site we want to start from. We can also add extra sites, by adding them after the first.

To get a come complete view we will need to add more sites.

Using [[Coffeehouse Culture]] as an example. As I write this, the latest version of this is on the 'wiki.parliamentofthings.org' site and there are 10 twins. But starting from [http://fedwiki.rodwell.me/narrative/#small-public-spaces@wiki.parliamentofthings.org there] we only see 4 sites.

Using [[Coffeehouse Culture]] as an example. As I write this, the latest version of this is on the 'jenny.uk.fedwikihappening.net' site and there are 8 twins, in my neighbourhood. But starting from [http://fedwiki.rodwell.me/narrative/#coffeehouse-culture@jenny.uk.fedwikihappening.net there] we only see 4 sites.
